name: Lislot_Bloodscar
content:
Lislot Bloodscar was a female Trandoshan who lived during the Galactic Civil War.
Lislot Bloodscar was a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
